        <h2>Soccer-Specific Planning</h2>
        <p>High school soccer teams typically range from 18-30 players. Many schools have separate boys' and girls' programs, meaning you may be coordinating multiple banquets or a combined celebration.</p>

        <h3>Soccer Decor Themes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Pitch Perfect</strong> — Field-themed decorations with netting, goal post accents, and green accents</li>
          <li><strong>World Cup Celebration</strong> — Flag-themed decorations representing the team's identity</li>
          <li><strong>Footy Fest</strong> — Casual, fun atmosphere with soccer balls as centerpiece elements</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="product-note">
          <p><strong>⚽ Soccer Ball Centerpieces:</strong> Custom 3D printed soccer ball centerpieces (8") in your team's colors with optional personalization. Classic pentagon-hexagon panel design, hand-painted to match your school colors. Makes a great banquet table topper that players love to take home.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/custom-soccer-ball-centerpiece-8-soccer-ball-graduation-party-birthday" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">View Soccer Centerpieces →</a>
        </div>

        <h2>Soccer Award Ideas</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Team MVP</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Golden Boot</strong> — Leading goal scorer</li>
          <li><strong>Golden Glove</strong> — Outstanding goalkeeper</li>
          <li><strong>Most Assists</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Defensive Anchor</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Most Improved</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Teammate of the Year</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Heart of the Team</strong> — Coach's award</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Combined Boys & Girls Banquets</h2>
        <p>If your school combines boys' and girls' soccer banquets, decide whether to present awards together (celebrating the whole soccer program) or separately (giving each team its moment). A combined slideshow with both teams' highlights works wonderfully.</p>

        <p><a href="/banquet-planning/" class="btn btn-outline">Full Banquet Guide →</a> <a href="/decorations/" class="btn btn-outline">Decoration Ideas →</a></p>
